        public final Bounds getAdmissibleDistanceBounds(TimePoint tpFrom,
                                 TimePoint tpTo)
        Gets the minimum and maximum allowed distance between a pair of TimePoints.
        Parameters:
        tpFrom - the TimePoint that is considered as the "origin"/source.
        tpTo - the TimePoint that is considered as the "target".
        Returns:
        Returns the bounds of the distance between the two TimePoints or null if there is no constraint between the two.
